{"tid":744774,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone9","createTime":"2018-07-16T07:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T15:57:24.000Z","uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f33eb466b371bfa6e4ef5c6902d7dade4af3d61d","tid":744774,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"中國報注意:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7098/3254221?utm_source=udnplus&amp;utm_medium=fb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7098%2F3254221%3Futm_source%3Dudnplus%26utm_medium%3Dfb&d=Hsg6bBXkDCZF%2F1K4r0b0JQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e927188b\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7098/3254221?utm_source=udnplus&amp;utm_medium=fb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone 9無邊框只要1.8萬元 5大特色值得期待<br />\n分享留言列印<br />\nA-A+<br />\n2018-07-15 22:16聯合新聞網 綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n傳為蘋果2018年6.1吋LCD版新款iPhone。 圖擷自technobezz<br />\n傳為蘋果2018年6.1吋LCD版新款iPhone。 圖擷自technobezz<br />\n蘋果新iPhone 9月將登場，外界預計今年將推出三款新iPhone，6.1吋LCD螢幕和6.5吋、5.8吋OLED螢幕款式，其中最被注目的6.1吋低價版被視為iPhone 9，根據騰訊新聞指出「5大值得期待的特色」，包括：無邊框設計、Face ID、螢幕亮度提升、多種顏色能選擇、價格具有吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n無邊框設計<br />\n由於產品定位的關係，iPhone 9採用的是液晶LCD螢幕，而非配iPhone X的高價位OLED螢幕，不過此次三款新iPhone，蘋果會盡量縮小設計上的差異，讓iPhone 9的做工有質感。根據外媒爆料，iPhone 9將採用JDI半柔性LCD螢幕，以及新型LED面板，以縮減邊框厚度，讓螢幕寬度僅比iPhone X稍微寬一點點，瀏海螢幕蠻可能會保留下來。<br />\n<br />\nFace ID<br />\n今年3款新iPhone都有臉部辨識功能，蘋果的3D結構光技術仍是業界最先進的技術，今年就算沒有大的升級，仍會領先OPPO Find X等機型。<br />\n<br />\n另外，飛時測距（TOF）3D臉部識別解決方案未量產，存在不確定性。而A12處理器可能具備更好的臉部識別算法，面容ID應該會更安全、更快、覆蓋範圍更廣。<br />\n<br />\n螢幕亮度提升<br />\niPhone 9的JDI半柔性LCD螢幕是LG製造機率高，可以期待「MLCD+」顯示技術，使螢幕除了RGB三色外，還外加一個白色像素點，讓螢幕亮度大幅提升，就像LG的G7的螢幕亮度是1000尼特。<br />\n<br />\n另外，知名蘋果分析師郭明錤預測iPhone 9可能取消3D Touch功能，但外掛式觸控模組（CGS）卻也多了一片薄膜感應器，達到減少螢幕厚度與成本。<br />\n<br />\n多種顏色能選擇<br />\n據3C達人Steve H.（@OnLeaks）消息，iPhone 9的配色蘋果已測試白色、黑色（太空灰）、紅色、黃色、藍色、橘色和粉紅色等，看似多樣化但實際推出的可能會少一些，量產機率最高的可能是紅色、黃色和藍色這3種。<br />\n<br />\n價格具吸引力<br />\n郭明錤曾表示美國未稅單機價格在600～700美元之間（約新台幣1.8萬～2.1萬元），且iPhone 9具全螢幕無邊框、Face ID，吸引力絕對比去年換湯不換藥的iPhone 8更強大，極度看好銷售量。"},{"pid":"ae5a92da7965a45c2f0f2f60639bad3bcd7225b7","tid":744774,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"我想要touch id <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547c7f2ecc9201351e662acfd3c8c72193edcc67","tid":744774,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"1.8萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw假新聞"},{"pid":"305d3d5a3522e1a42d5136527e6263a6f0790910","tid":744774,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"547c7f2ecc9201351e662acfd3c8c72193edcc67","tid":744774,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"1.8萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br /